  "remarks": "Sentenced to life without parole in the Philippines on 23 Jan. 2009 for his involvement in the bombings of 30 Dec. 2000 in Manila, the Philippines. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 25 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Photos included in INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:\nhttps://www.interpol.int/en/notice/search/un/1427252.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 9 September 2003 (amended on 9 Sep. 2005, 23 Feb. 2009, 3 Jun. 2009, 16 May 2011, 22 Sep. 2017, 24 Nov. 2020)",
